{"type":"message","id":"8cd7af47","parentId":"0aa3b69d","timestamp":"2026-02-25T08:30:57.704Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:e98293b9-d311-43c8-9e94-61eb5b4792fa task:e98293b9-d311-43c8-9e94-61eb5b4792fa] 继续诊断 kuroneko.chat 登录 API 的 500 错误。\n\n## 背景\n- 空请求返回正常 JSON（\"邮箱和密码不能为空\"）\n- 但用户实际登录时遇到 500 INTERNAL SERVER ERROR\n- 服务器 IP: 43.156.244.45\n\n## 继续诊断\n\n### 1. 测试不同请求格式\n```bash\n# 测试 form-data 格式\ncurl -X POST https://kuroneko.chat/api/auth/login \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded\" \\\n  -d \"email=test@test.com&password=test123\"\n\n# 测试 JSON 格式\ncurl -X POST https://kuroneko.chat/api/auth/login \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"email\":\"test@test.com\",\"password\":\"test123\"}'\n\n# 测试不同字段名\ncurl -X POST https://kuroneko.chat/api/auth/login \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"username\":\"test@test.com\",\"password\":\"test123\"}'\n```\n\n### 2. 检查服务端代码\n```bash\n# 查找小说项目的后端代码\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace/novel-project -name \"*.js\" -o -name \"*.ts\" | head -20\n\n# 查找登录相关代码\ngrep -r \"auth/login\" /root/.openclaw/workspace/novel-project/ 2>/dev/null\ngrep -r \"login\" /root/.openclaw/workspace/novel-project/server/ 2>/dev/null | head -20\n```\n\n### 3. 检查服务器状态\n```bash\n# 尝试直接 SSH 到 IP\nssh -o ConnectTimeout=10 -o StrictHostKeyChecking=no root@43.156.244.45 \"uptime && docker ps\"\n\n# 检查服务器上的服务\nssh root@43.156.244.45 \"systemctl status novel-api 2>/dev/null || pm2 list 2>/dev/null || docker logs novel-api 2>/dev/null | tail -50\"\n```\n\n### 4. 检查数据库连接\n```bash\n# 如果能连接服务器，检查数据库\nssh root@43.156.244.45 \"docker exec novel-db mysql -e 'SELECT 1' 2>/dev/null || docker exec novel-db psql -c 'SELECT 1' 2>/dev/null\"\n```\n\n### 5. 查看最近的错误日志\n```bash\n# 查找本地是否有日志文件\nfind /root/.openclaw/workspace -name \"*.log\" -mtime -1 2>/dev/null\n\n# 如果能连接服务器\nssh root@43.156.244.45 \"tail -100 /var/log/novel/error.log 2>/dev/null || journalctl -u novel-api --since '1 hour ago' 2>/dev/null\"\n```\n\n## 输出\n1. 哪种请求格式触发 500 错误\n2. 服务器端日志（如果能获取）\n3. 数据库连接状态\n4. 问题根因和修复方案\nCurrent time: Wednesday, February 25th, 2026 — 4:30 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772008257702}}
